Predefined Exercise Type

Samsung Digital Health predefines common exercise types.

If you want to see your application's exercise data on S Health, set the EXERCISE_TYPE property of data and write it to S Health. S Health shows exercise data that the EXERCISE_TYPE property is specified.

The following table includes all predefined exercise types. Use the value of the Exercise type column to set the EXERCISE_TYPE property.

Some exercise types are exceptional and they are not shown on S Health because of the S Health's policy. Though inserted exercise data is not shown on S Health, it doesn't mean that your application's data is not saved to S Health. You can check the data with the DataViewer tool of the SDK.

If there is no matched exercise type with your application's exercise data, set the EXERCISE_TYPE property with 0 and define ERCISE_CUSTOM_TYPE.
